  "text": "## SmartSaver Plus  \n**Q: What is SmartSaver Plus?**\nA: Premium tier of SmartSaver for larger balances (£50,001+). Earns 5.25% interest (vs. standard tier at 4.80%).  \n**Q: Who qualifies for SmartSaver Plus?**\nA: Account holders with balance over £50,001.  \n**Q: What are the extra benefits?**\nA:\n- Higher interest rate (5.25% vs. 4.80%)\n- Dedicated account manager\n- Priority customer service\n- No international transfer fees  \n**Q: How do I upgrade to Plus?**\nA: Automatic when your balance exceeds £50,001. No application needed.  \n**Q: What if my balance drops below £50,001?**\nA: You'll drop back to standard SmartSaver rates (4.80% for Tier 3). Can upgrade again anytime your balance exceeds £50,001.  \n---",
